Best practices and troubleshooting
- Distinguish TypeError (wrong type) vs RangeError (value out of allowed range) to make error handling clearer for callers.
- When catching errors across legacy environments, test instance via `error instanceof RangeError` and `error.name === 'RangeError'` for robustness.

